ml_tags: ‘Efeso 2 : 8 - 10 He ko e kelesi pē kuo mou mo‘ui mei ai, ‘io, na‘e ‘ikai meiate kimoutolu ia, ko e me‘a ‘i ho‘omou tui; ka ko e foaki mei he ‘Otua:  na‘e ‘ikai tupu mei ha ngaahi ngāue, koe‘uhi ke ‘oua na‘a ai ha taha ‘e fa‘a pōlepole. He ko ‘ene ngaohi ‘a kitautolu, kuo fakatupu ‘ia Kalaisi Sīsū ke fai ‘a e ngaahi ngāue lelei, ‘a ia na‘e toka teuteu ‘e he ‘Otua ke tau fou ai.
